<br>
If you regen a Fade in 10min you obviously have a standing manaregen of 9 mana/tick.  That means you either have BaMR and at least 2 FT, or 6 FT...  Any combination of which I consider to be beyond &quot;the average non-raiding Bard&quot;.<br>
<br>
---<br>
<br>
